      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury SUV offers the perfect balance of sophisticated performance and everyday utility. Finished in a deep Obsidian Black, the exterior retains a high gloss, showing only minor road wear and a few faint stone chips consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the premium saddle leather cabin remains supple and smoke-free, with all electronic features\u2014including the panoramic sunroof and navigation system\u2014functioning flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, featuring a recent oil change, fresh brake pads, and a brand-new set of all-season tires. While not a showroom floor model, its mechanical reliability and pristine interior make it a standout choice for a discerning buyer. Complete service records are available upon request.",
      "price": 36500.0,
