      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been a dream. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-cared for over the years\u2014runs smooth and still looks fantastic pulling into the driveway. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for many more adventures, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
